      <c01 level="series">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Prints</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Photographic Prints series is comprised of photographs that document the social activities the society organized with the young female members between 1940 and 1960. The pictures depict young girls dressed in costume for Halloween celebrations, picnics, and other social events. While some of the prints have captions, none of them include the names of the individuals in the photographs.</p>
        </scopecontent>
